Student Project – Scope of Work (SOW)
Project Title: Car Garage Manager
Student Name: Andrew Bouris
Date: 7/16/25

1. Project Overview
My Car Garage Manager will be a basic program that could be used by car dealerships or people with large garages to organize data of their vehicles. 
For this program specifically, users will be able to add, remove, search for, and display vehicles, and all data will be saved to a text file so it is available to see the next time the program is opened.

2. Features
Add a new car
Display all cars
Display information about car
Search by make or model
Remove a car
Save data to a file
Load data from a file


